@node Main "Konnex - Documentation"

                              'Konnex' V1.0

                           by Charles-N. Jacob

  'Konnex' is a @{" Workbench game " link play} where you have to connect all
tiles of the game board, by rotating these so they connect with
neighbouring tiles. However, just to complicate matters a little,
only a small portion (a 5 by 5 tile area) of the board is visible...

  Two types of tiles are shown in the display: 'central' tiles,
indicated by their 'embossed' borders, which can be rotated, and
those that are located around the central tiles, which allow you
to move on the game board.

  Complete each game board in the least amount of moves.

  Have fun!

